    "faq_product": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "pq1": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What does the lip ganache smell like?",
            "text": "<p>Each flavour is scented to match its dessert namesake using food-grade fragrance oils that are safe for lip application. Raspberry Coulis smells like raspberry, Hot Cocoa smells like cocoa and vanilla, and so on.<\/p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "pq2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it safe for sensitive lips?",
            "text": "<p>Our lip ganache is formulated with gentle, vegan ingredients. However, if you have known sensitivities or allergies, we recommend checking the full ingredient list on the product label or contacting us before purchase.<\/p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "pq3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long does the colour last?",
            "text": "<p>The soft satin finish typically lasts 3–4 hours with normal wear. For longer-lasting colour, apply two coats and blot between layers. Reapply after eating or drinking.<\/p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "pq4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are all ingredients vegan?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, 100%. Every ingredient in our lip ganache formula is vegan and cruelty-free. We never test on animals at any stage of development.<\/p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "pq5": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What's the Lip Balm Charm bundle deal?",
            "text": "<p>When you purchase any Lip Ganache from the Sweet Treat collection, you can add a Lip Balm Charm (Silver or Gold) for $18 instead of the regular price of $22. The discount applies automatically at checkout.<\/p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        }
      },
